title: PlayStation Delists Cyberpunk 2077 - Kinda Funny Games Daily 12.18.20
description:
Greg and Imran deliver the final Kinda Funny Games Daily of the year as CD Projekt continues to burn. #cyberpunk2077

00:00:00 - Start
00:05:00 - Housekeeping
Our Back 4 Blood let’s play is up on youtube.com/kindafunnygames!
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Black Jack
The Roper Report   -

00:30:20 - is this going too far? - Best Friends Q:The Other Shaun
00:36:45 - Is the most disappointing generation ever? - Best Friends Q:Matt From Edmonton
00:49:48 -  Ad

01:06:40 - Squad Up:Mark Freeman(Zoom/Twitter) - @theindieboy1
01:07:00 - You‘re Wrong
Kinda Funny Day - Monday, January 4th @ 10 am PT - 12 Hours
